{"tid":2512624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中國同香港真心唔差，不過我今年內都會BNO移民過英國","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T03:02:21.000Z","uid":175215,"like":19,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbde46be05f61e790e95ad08ac5cc63bb689bc0","tid":2512624,"uid":175215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:24:25.000Z","msg":"其實中國同香港真心唔差，不過我今年內都會移民過英國<br />\n<br />\n講真好同唔好睇你用咩心態去<br />\n1: 中國發展迅速係事實（人地外國d工廠下下出糧比d員工係幾咁on9, 學下中國新疆啦，捉你入去比飯你食比洗腦教育就已經要多謝黨），生意成本完全無得同中國鬥<br />\n2:冇民主自由亦都係事實,中國大部份人根本就唔想要民主自由，最緊要有國家夠強大，可以攞黎比中國平民用黎打飛機。<br />\n（ 就好似d人返麥當勞出緊最低工資都仲可以同人講自己間公司幾撚勁一樣，幾撚值得自豪呀）開開心心又1日。<br />\n<br />\n但當我六年之後入左籍既時候黎返又可以享受國家嘅強大，轉個撚頭又可以享受民主自由。 簡直無得輸。 <br />\n依家已經開始明白有雙重國籍既人點解會咁爱国了。"},{"pid":"c54f7a6b18d272a713483a8200baf53ebeb8744c","tid":2512624,"uid":310700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"曲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ad2a816fe3e190e4c2d930a6fafb6b074e0ca6","tid":2512624,"uid":4857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:29:07.000Z","msg":"雖然曲，但第二點真心認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078fbdf114e835466212976e650161306f7b500d","tid":2512624,"uid":175215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:37:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2afeb0e01781c251a60cd4a87001ff675ed24f","tid":2512624,"uid":10621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />